Navigate crazy obstacle courses in pursuit of your holy parking spot in this 80s Arcade Style driving game. 
Tempt fate & physics as you navigate obstacle courses in pursuit of your holy parking spot in this 80s retro environment in Try Hard Parking! . Put your driving skills to the test in this retro styled game as you jump,drop and carefully steer across levels full of obstacle to reach your holy parking lot. 
Features: 10 Unique Crazy Levels with Different Vehicles ranging from 80s known Cars to A-Team's Van. Difficult, Fun, Fast, Frustrating and Rage Inducing Gameplay with great music to keep your cool. Game Trophies such as "Grand ma" for slowest and "Takumi 86" for Fastest or "Super Tuber" for extreme players. System Requirements: 
Windows X/ Vista/ 7/ 8/ 10; Videocard: Nvidia 9400M or ATi/AMD HD 2400 or Intel HD 4000 Publisher:
